{
  "texts": [
    "In Study 3 we incentivized users to produce better reappraisals.",
    "While incentivized participants spent more time on their reappraisals, the gap in reappraisal quality between humans and GPT-4 did not change, suggesting that the source of the difference is more associated with skill and not effort.",
    "In Study 4, we manipulated whether participants were informed or not about the source of reappraisal, showing the label of the source of reappraisal impacted raters' evaluation of the effectiveness of the reappraisal when the source was GPT-4 but not humans.",
    "We conducted three different analyses of the text to further explore the difference between human and GPT-4 reappraisals.",
    "First, we showed that humans and GPT-4 don't differ in how semantically close they are to the actual vignettes they are reappraising."
  ]
}